:grimacing: I really don't like this...

Could we maybe instead change the `border: 2px solid darkred` to only apply on the root Mermaid SVG, maybe with something like:

```css
div.mermaid svg:first-of-type {
  border: 2px solid darkred;
}
```

(FYI, I'm not a CSS expert, so I have no idea if the above will work!)

